Package yeezus.memory

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Memory
    A storage mechanism for Words in the yeezus operating system.
    MMU
    The MMU helps organize the RAM Memory in the yeezus Operating System.
    Word
    A stand-in version of a word (4 bytes) that will be the basis of the memory system in the yeezus OS.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidAddressException
    To be thrown if the Memory attempts to access an invalid memory location.
    InvalidWordException
    To be thrown if invalid values are passed to the constructor of Word.
